HEADWORD: Equitableness
<hw>Eq"ui*ta*ble*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality of being
equitable, just, or impartial; <as>as, the <ex>equitableness</ex> of a
judge, a decision, or distribution of property</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Equitably</ent>⟦br⟧
